<inglise> of 31 March 1999 amending Regulation (EC) No 504/97 laying down detailed rules for the application of Council Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 as regards the system of production aid for products processed from fruit and vegetables </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 702/1999, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 504/97, milles s&auml;testatakse n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 2201/96 &uuml;ksikasjalikud rakenduseeskirjad seoses puu- ja k&ouml;&ouml;giviljatoodete tootmistoetuste s&uuml;steemiga 31. m&auml;rts 1999 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 of 28 October 1996 on the common organisation of the markets in processed fruit and vegetable products(1), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 2199/97(2), and in particular Article 4(9) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 28. oktoobri 1996. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 2201/96 puu- ja k&ouml;&ouml;giviljatooteturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 2199/97, (2) eriti selle artikli 4 l&otilde;iget 9, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 6(3) of Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 lays down that the quotas for each group of products shall be shared out each year among the Member States according to the average quantities produced in compliance with minimum prices during the preceding three marketing years; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 2201/96 artikli 6 l&otilde;ikes 3 s&auml;testatakse, et iga tooter&uuml;hma kvoodid jagatakse liikmesriikide vahel igal aastal vastavalt eelneva kolme majandusaasta jooksul miinimumhindadega toodetud keskmistele kogustele; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 6(1) of Commission Regulation (EC) No 504/97(3), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1590/98(4), provides for a preliminary contract to be drawn up for products processed from tomatoes to be concluded by 16 February each year; whereas the Member States may defer that date to 16 March; whereas Article 11(4) of that Regulation lays down that production aid applications must be submitted to the competent authorities by 1 February of the marketing year concerned; whereas Article 17(2) lays down that the Member States must notify the Commission by 1 April each year of the final figures for the marketing year concerned; </inglise>
<eesti> komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 504/97 (3) (viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1590/98 (4)) artikli 6 l&otilde;ikega 1 n&auml;hakse ette tomatitooteid k&auml;sitleva eellepingu s&otilde;lmimine enne iga aasta 16. veebruari; liikmesriigid v&otilde;ivad selle t&auml;htaja 16. m&auml;rtsini edasi l&uuml;kata; k&otilde;nealuse m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 11 l&otilde;ikes 4 s&auml;testatakse, et tootmistoetuse taotlused tuleb esitada p&auml;devale asutusele asjaomase majandusaasta 1. veebruariks; artikli 17 l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatakse, et liikmesriigid peavad teatama komisjonile iga aasta 1. aprilliks asjaomase majandusaasta l&otilde;plikud n&auml;itajad; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the figures for each marketing year are only available from 1 April; whereas the allocation of quotas provided for in Article 6(3) of Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 cannot therefore be carried out in time to sign preliminary contracts; whereas it is therefore necessary to bring forward the date for submission of aid applications to the competent authorities to the 15 December of the marketing year concerned; </inglise>
<eesti> iga majandusaasta puhul on n&auml;itajad k&auml;ttesaadavad alles alates 1. aprillist; seep&auml;rast ei saa m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 2201/96 artikli 6 l&otilde;ikega 3 etten&auml;htud kvoote jagada ajaks, mis on vajalik eellepingute s&otilde;lmimise v&otilde;imaldamiseks; seep&auml;rast tuleb p&auml;devale asutusele toetustaotluste esitamise t&auml;htaeg viia asjaomase majandusaasta 15. detsembrile; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in view of the above change, it is necessary to adapt certain provisions of Regulation (EC) No 504/97 to this new situation, particularly the date by which the final figures for the marketing year must be notified to the Commission, the deadline for signing preliminary contracts, their submission to the competent authorities of the Member States and the notification of these contracts to the Commission; </inglise>
<eesti> eespool nimetatud muudatust silmas pidades tuleb uue olukorra tarvis kohandada teatavaid m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 504/97 s&auml;tteid, eriti majandusaasta l&otilde;plike n&auml;itajate komisjonile teatamise t&auml;htaega ning eellepingute allkirjastamise, nende liikmesriikide p&auml;devatele asutustele esitamise ja k&otilde;nealustest lepingutest komisjonile teatamise t&auml;htaega; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for products processed from fruit and vegetables, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las puu- ja k&ouml;&ouml;giviljatooteturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
