<inglise> In the case of tomatoes, preliminary contracts shall be concluded each year, pending the conclusion of contracts as referred to in Article 7(1), at the most 10 working days from the publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities of the allocation of quotas for each group of products between the Member States." </inglise>
<eesti> Tomatite puhul s&otilde;lmitakse artikli 7 l&otilde;ikes 1 osutatud lepingutele eelnevad eellepingud igal aastal hiljemalt k&uuml;mme t&ouml;&ouml;p&auml;eva p&auml;rast iga tooter&uuml;hma kvootide liikmesriikide vahel jaotamise teadaande avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas." </eesti>
<inglise> (2) Article 11(4) is replaced by the following: </inglise>
